trans-unit.source: A persistence command that lets you save instance state information into the persistence store.
trans-unit.target: En utholdenhet kommando som brukes til å lagre informasjon om forekomsten til vedvarende lager.

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.DurableInstancing.SaveWorkflowCommand"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Activities.DurableInstancing.SaveWorkflowCommand"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Sets the status of the instance in the persistence database to “Completed” and deletes the state information from the database unless the <xref:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.SqlWorkflowInstanceStore.InstanceCompletionAction*> property is set to “Delete Nothing”.
trans-unit.target: Angir status for forekomsten i utholdenhet databasen til "Fullført" og sletter tilstandsinformasjonen fra databasen, med mindre den <xref:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.SqlWorkflowInstanceStore.InstanceCompletionAction*>er satt til "Slette ingenting".</xref:System.Activities.DurableInstancing.SqlWorkflowInstanceStore.InstanceCompletionAction*>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the status of the instance is “Completed” and the state information is deleted; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis statusen for forekomsten er slettet "Fullført" og tilstandsinformasjonen; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the instance data to be saved into the persistence store.
trans-unit.target: Henter forekomstdataene lagres til vedvarende lager.

trans-unit.target: Inneholder forekomst nøkler som må være knyttet til en forekomst.
